<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>If everyone, the government and everyday folks, would take some time and think about the full ramifactions of their actions, good and bad, then the world would be a very different place. These people didn't see this comming. Some had been there 30 years...they walk in the door ready to start work and boom. Here's your pinkslip..now fuck off. I'm sure it wouldn't have been as hard with some warning.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
